Right now, there are so many fools that know nothing except
&quot;Go to meetings, get a sponsor, and work the Steps&quot;.
<p>
Did you read
<a href="orange-intro.html" target="_blank">the introduction</a>,
where I learned that my Stepper counselor was snorting
cocaine and screwing his step-children while he taught us how to be &quot;spiritual&quot;?
That's your competition. You can hardly do worse.
Now go out there and beat the pants off of the competition!
(Sorry for the pun.)
<p>
And have a good day.
<p>
Orange
